-- Thai Siam Commercial Bank sees 2014 home loan growth of 7 pct     
-- By Manunphattr Dhanananphorn
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 03:57AM EDT
-- None



BANGKOK, Aug 5 (Reuters) - Siam Commercial Cank Pcl <SCB.BK>, Thailand's third-largest lender, said on Tuesday it expected 2014 housing loans to grow 7 percent on the year on expectations that economic recovery would spur demand in the second half of the year.

